Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:01.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:04.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋 昨天你無視我郵件了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:05.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看啊 每天都問「你在幹什麼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你還敢說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我和千秋 交往已經快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:16.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到現在為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:20.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還沒 親過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香奈還沒過接吻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.33,0:01:28.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為才一年呀 這才要開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:31.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會太晚了嗎 千秋君什麼都沒做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:33.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那傢伙並沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:36.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 真是拉了好大一坨屎哇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你這個屎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 誰都會拉大便的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是來氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:47.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,回想起來我們之間比起戀人可能更像兄妹一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 千秋 我們關係挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:54.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗶~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哇 被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,倒是挺有默契呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:00.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,很合拍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:05.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吶 千秋你覺得這樣就好嗎 我們之間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:06.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:11.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想要更加親密一點 肌膚接觸這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:13.81,comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}備註：相撲開始時裁判的吆喝聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是啦 更加像戀愛一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你早說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好過分 在玩弄我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,呀 不是開玩笑 而是更正經的 接吻什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這還是太羞恥了吧 明明沒有在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也很害羞啊 但姑且算戀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:35.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:38.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說到底和我做那什麼真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:43.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啥?誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 等一下 我們什麼開始交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,去年的春天我不是告白了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,放學回家路上!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.95,0:03:00.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我…我喜歡千秋君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 我也喜歡你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:07.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我以為那是在演小品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我就覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋都不跟我牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是平時看起來只是摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:15.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我以為只是害羞啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算是這樣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,近距離感受到了千秋君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我們之間的距離明明很近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:26.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,(感情卻)一點都沒有傳達到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 幹嘛哭成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只有我自以為是地認為是女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,堅持發著郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,親暱地…打你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 我們好好交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,搞什麼 又是開玩笑?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是啊 我也有過當你男朋友的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我看不懂你的心思 於是一直沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:55.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 喜歡你 認真交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:58.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要不停給我發郵件的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,再打你也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:07.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:13.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以下次再和我 演小品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟喜歡的人告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,糟透了 回去睡覺好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞 松浦這就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,欸 社團活動呢 翹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,偷懶? 咦 翹了? 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:40.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,香取前輩 我今天身體不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊勒 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看你很悲傷的樣子還以為你肯定是失戀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:50.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 說? 中? 了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,問了不該問的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:55.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:57.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是你拿出了勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這就已經很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你現在的樣子 最棒地閃耀著唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你把我當傻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,完全沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我只是想給你打打氣而已 生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算不給我打氣也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:19.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是你的心在哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 一不小心手就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,隨你盡情地揍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:27.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:31.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是你真正想揍的 是你自己不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然在把我當傻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:41.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且揍完我之後舒暢多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩是因為這個才故意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,雖然依舊沒有半點想感激他的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,以後還有什麼煩惱儘管跟我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:51.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 並不需要 說起來為什麼要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 學長 妳 學妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:54.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:57.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好了 這下可以去社團活動了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:58.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:04.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前輩雖然很煩人但基本上算是個好人吶 雖然很煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我家的偶像要不在的話多寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:08.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有 請不要看著這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 難道迷上我了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我太耀眼了真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯?怎麼了?嗯?這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,被喜歡的女生 喊出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.07,0:06:33.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下次可以一起吃個飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦!? 和我?為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想著作為之前受你照顧的回禮之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,添麻煩了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也沒有添麻煩就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:45.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,太好了 那星期天 等你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:48.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦咦咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那麼可愛的為什麼要和我這醜男…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來太早了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,她是一位常和我乘同輛公車的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我雖一直悄悄地喜歡著她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但一直沒有上前搭話的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊! 痴漢!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喔喔喔! 早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真巧呢!  栗原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最 最近高嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:24.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 最近好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:29.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,從那時起應該被她關注到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但沒想到居然想回禮什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說來真的會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那種人怎麼想也不會約我出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒錯肯定都是我的腦補 好 結案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 超可愛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 被你這麼看著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 才沒有看你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也完全沒覺得可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不對! 雖然覺得很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對! 是衣服!衣服超可愛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不對 不只是衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是山根同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一起去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我請客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:07:59.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這種時候該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,太貴的地方也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哪裡有又便宜又好吃的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那蕎麥麵之類的怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那邊就有站著吃的麵館…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:10.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我來決定可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,請不要客氣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:19.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要不點個自助飲品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不…不用了 吃完就馬上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:26.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我也不是說我想回去!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,可以的話 想一直在一起之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊! 這話很噁心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 不要緊 我馬上就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:40.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我每天早上都有在關注山根同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:44.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你總是給老人讓座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有 有時候得做點好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼說 我存在感這麼低!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 幫助我時的山根同學 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,讓你想起糟糕的回憶 對不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:59.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是有多廢啊! 難得人家特意約我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,山根同學真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 說我長相嗎? 經常被這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,長相也很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,平 平安時代的話說不定如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,現在是平成啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 是玩笑話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道是作為吉祥物來看很優秀嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:21.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是吧 這認真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是吧 不不 對我這種人怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我這邊可是一直被女生無視的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,別被騙了! 這種事情不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果 可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是期待一下都要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是萬一是真的怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:36.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,請和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等等 我內心的準備還…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:39.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:42.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,追加兩份自助飲品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:50.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天值日的人回去了 麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:51.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:59.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同班的菅原君 最近能夠說上話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一個人在做清潔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:03.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一個人的話很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我去拿掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.74,0:10:10.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 菅原今天值日? 訓練開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:18.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊菅原君 要是有部門的訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:24.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都說沒事 是我想幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,居然這麼想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道菅原君你 特愛乾淨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你經常幫忙做清潔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不… 也沒有經常就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天 那個 怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:36.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為是高野…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好像有什麼難言之隱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道 我清潔做的很差??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉… 那我安靜掃地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:47.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 嗯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道我的感情暴露了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 我並沒有奇怪的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:56.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,或者說 對不起讓你在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:59.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是我沒有注意到 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦? 怎麼做? 做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實不用替我操心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因為在意我（的清潔）才來幫我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:10.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實我一直很在意高野你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 我一直沒被教過這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 我也沒被教過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說起來 高野你 準備怎麼辦的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我想變得更加熟練
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,熟練? 咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:30.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為了能（掃得）更加漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我覺得 現在就足夠漂亮了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是嗎 那要怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我對高野你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:43.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 可能是我太心急了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,慢慢來就好 我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說 是效率的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我太慢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:52.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才沒有那種事!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實 我一直是急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天只要我能傳達出我的感情就 真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}下次 我等著高野你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝 我也會儘快變得熟練的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:02.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,做清潔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這麼難說出口的話也願意和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然菅原君你是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊不 現在我們在說啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是在討論做清潔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,阿勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒錯! 是的! 做清潔 清潔!
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也會覺得很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}此時此刻也在想念著你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}喜歡與討厭相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的機率的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}還是跨不出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}我們的關係可以說是曖昧模糊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}雖然無聊但還是希望能感受到屬於我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}要珍視這份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
