Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.75,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.26,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.09,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.56,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:52.94,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:58.36,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.91,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:10.08,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:15.96,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
