Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.58,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}逐漸淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.75,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你的面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:41.26,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}害怕這逐漸的  忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.09,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}只是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.56,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想把這份風景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:52.94,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}鎖進我的心裡  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:58.36,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想與你相見這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.91,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}卻很需要勇氣  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:10.08,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:15.96,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明天當我  睜開眼的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:22.05,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你能在我身旁而已
